title: Gregory Benford - Tides of Light (Galactic Center Saga #4)
description:
Gregory Benford - Tides of Light (Galactic Center Saga #4)

Format: MP3
Unabridged

Continuing the story begun in Great Sky River, Benford creates a stunning novel of the last band of humans fleeing extinction in the Galactic Center. And with one enemy behind them, the humans are dismayed to discover on a remote planet an alien race more awesome than any they have encountered
